1
00:00:01,000 --> 00:00:04,000
{\an8}<b><font color="#9CD5FF">One Pace Premium</font></b>
Keep the project alive: <font color="#a8c7fa">ko-fi.com/not6ip</font>

2
00:01:49,960 --> 00:01:56,300
The Leaders

3
00:01:52,340 --> 00:01:55,300
Move it! Move it! Move it!
Move it! Move it!

4
00:01:55,300 --> 00:01:56,300
U-Up ahead...!

5
00:02:03,650 --> 00:02:05,310
Please wait, Commander Chaka!

6
00:02:08,900 --> 00:02:10,110
Who the hell are they?

7
00:02:10,530 --> 00:02:11,650
It's...

8
00:02:12,030 --> 00:02:13,490
...the Kicking Claw Force!

9
00:02:15,990 --> 00:02:20,120
Kicking Claw Force
Alabasta's Elite Guard Unit

10
00:02:23,330 --> 00:02:24,830
Don't attack!

11
00:02:25,460 --> 00:02:28,170
Stay away from this man!

12
00:02:31,800 --> 00:02:33,970
The Kicking Claw Force broke through!

13
00:02:33,970 --> 00:02:35,090
Of course they would!

14
00:02:35,090 --> 00:02:37,260
Please save the king and Princess Vivi!

15
00:02:38,260 --> 00:02:39,560
Your Majesty!

16
00:02:40,010 --> 00:02:43,980
Our duty is to defend you
to our dying breaths.

17
00:02:43,980 --> 00:02:46,060
We simply cannot
turn away from this man.

18
00:02:46,810 --> 00:02:49,320
He's one of the Seven
Warlords of the Sea.

19
00:02:49,320 --> 00:02:52,320
We'll do whatever it takes,
even if we have to play dirty.

20
00:02:52,820 --> 00:02:54,530
– All four of us...
– All four of us...

21
00:02:55,030 --> 00:02:56,700
...will fight together...

22
00:02:57,120 --> 00:02:58,530
...to set things right.

23
00:02:59,660 --> 00:03:02,660
I see that you've amassed
quite the following.

24
00:03:02,660 --> 00:03:04,250
In that case...

25
00:03:04,250 --> 00:03:06,790
I'll spare you, so run off and go home.

26
00:03:06,790 --> 00:03:08,750
No can do.

27
00:03:09,460 --> 00:03:12,260
There's a reason
that we can't withdraw.

28
00:03:12,840 --> 00:03:14,510
A reason?

29
00:03:16,680 --> 00:03:21,760
If you really are the ringleader
of this rebellion, then we must...

30
00:03:25,730 --> 00:03:26,980
Those bruises...!

31
00:03:29,190 --> 00:03:30,730
Is that what I think it is?!

32
00:03:34,990 --> 00:03:35,950
Shall I?

33
00:03:35,950 --> 00:03:38,700
Don't bother. They're vermin.

34
00:03:41,870 --> 00:03:42,660
They didn't...

35
00:03:46,000 --> 00:03:47,210
Chaka!

36
00:03:47,210 --> 00:03:48,880
Something is wrong with them!

37
00:03:48,880 --> 00:03:51,960
To temporarily boost their power...

38
00:03:52,920 --> 00:03:54,920
they drank the hero elixir,

39
00:03:55,550 --> 00:03:57,800
a deadly potion.

40
00:03:57,800 --> 00:04:00,600
They only have
a few minutes left to live.

41
00:04:00,970 --> 00:04:02,310
They can't be saved...

42
00:04:02,310 --> 00:04:03,970
Oh no!

43
00:04:05,980 --> 00:04:09,350
I thought as much...

44
00:04:09,350 --> 00:04:12,940
Challenging me at the cost
of your own lives...?

45
00:04:13,650 --> 00:04:15,190
Commander Chaka,

46
00:04:15,190 --> 00:04:18,360
please forgive us for doing this
without consulting you.

47
00:04:18,360 --> 00:04:19,910
However, we have to make him...

48
00:04:20,740 --> 00:04:23,280
understand this country's... pain!

49
00:04:41,970 --> 00:04:44,310
You... fools...

50
00:04:45,140 --> 00:04:47,730
We have to make him...

51
00:04:47,770 --> 00:04:49,480
realize this country's...

52
00:04:54,480 --> 00:04:56,980
anger!

53
00:05:11,540 --> 00:05:13,790
You didn't think this through.

54
00:05:14,460 --> 00:05:17,130
You should value your lives.

55
00:05:17,760 --> 00:05:19,630
But it's too late for that, right?

56
00:05:25,930 --> 00:05:30,430
If you're about to die anyway,
that saves me the trouble, doesn't it?

57
00:05:30,810 --> 00:05:33,560
So you won't even battle them?!

58
00:05:49,870 --> 00:05:52,000
Commander... Chaka...

59
00:05:57,960 --> 00:06:01,470
This is the very definition of stupidity.

60
00:06:02,970 --> 00:06:04,840
You wretch!

61
00:06:08,390 --> 00:06:10,770
You bastard!

62
00:06:12,850 --> 00:06:14,020
Chaka!

63
00:06:14,400 --> 00:06:16,400
Chaka! Stop it!

64
00:06:16,400 --> 00:06:18,650
Don't follow them to their deaths!

65
00:06:19,070 --> 00:06:21,400
I see. A zoan type...

66
00:06:21,400 --> 00:06:25,450
Dog-Dog Fruit: Jackal!

67
00:06:26,280 --> 00:06:28,410
Howling Fangs!

68
00:06:32,370 --> 00:06:34,000
So you, too...

69
00:06:34,000 --> 00:06:35,500
would die...

70
00:06:36,830 --> 00:06:38,750
for the sake of others?

71
00:06:45,890 --> 00:06:51,100
Medi Assembly Hall's Front
Alubarna North Block

72
00:06:52,980 --> 00:06:54,100
Damn...

73
00:06:54,100 --> 00:06:55,730
I lost too much blood.

74
00:06:56,600 --> 00:06:59,820
I guess I'm lucky
that the wounds aren't deep...

75
00:06:59,820 --> 00:07:02,900
But still... he got me good.

76
00:07:04,860 --> 00:07:06,910
I wonder how the others are doing..

77
00:07:06,910 --> 00:07:09,330
They better not be dead...

78
00:07:09,330 --> 00:07:11,370
I wanna know what's going on...

79
00:07:11,990 --> 00:07:13,620
What?!

80
00:07:13,620 --> 00:07:17,830
I have to pair up with Eyelashes?!

81
00:07:17,830 --> 00:07:21,460
He's a camel, for crying out loud!

82
00:07:21,460 --> 00:07:24,510
Don't underestimate how weak I am!

83
00:07:24,820 --> 00:07:28,010
It was because you lost
the raffle! Suck it up!

84
00:07:28,010 --> 00:07:31,140
All right! Then promise me one thing:

85
00:07:31,140 --> 00:07:32,890
When we're in a pinch,

86
00:07:32,890 --> 00:07:34,640
make sure you save us, please!

87
00:07:34,640 --> 00:07:38,440
Gimme me a break.
I only rescue damsels.

88
00:07:40,730 --> 00:07:42,070
Usopp...

89
00:07:44,940 --> 00:07:46,400
Hey, Usopp.

90
00:07:46,400 --> 00:07:49,370
Why are you crying?

91
00:07:49,370 --> 00:07:52,540
Who's crying?! I'm not crying!

92
00:07:52,540 --> 00:07:54,660
You're the one who's crying!

93
00:07:54,660 --> 00:07:56,660
That makes no sense!

94
00:07:56,660 --> 00:07:58,370
But...

95
00:07:58,750 --> 00:08:01,000
That mole hag said...

96
00:08:01,000 --> 00:08:05,340
that Luffy's dead, so...

97
00:08:05,840 --> 00:08:07,800
I... I wonder if it's true...

98
00:08:08,550 --> 00:08:10,800
You guys believe that?

99
00:08:11,260 --> 00:08:14,140
Of course not!
Are you stupid or what?!

100
00:08:14,140 --> 00:08:16,930
Me neither! I don't believe it at all!

101
00:08:18,690 --> 00:08:20,310
I get it!

102
00:08:20,310 --> 00:08:24,690
Then we better hurry over
to the palace.

103
00:08:25,150 --> 00:08:29,570
Hold your snot
until the battle is over.

104
00:08:31,490 --> 00:08:32,660
Don't swallow it!

105
00:08:36,120 --> 00:08:38,040
Everyone... thank you.

106
00:08:38,790 --> 00:08:40,500
It's too early to thank us.

107
00:08:40,880 --> 00:08:44,380
He's right. Besides, if you
wanna thank pirates...

108
00:08:44,380 --> 00:08:46,260
you have to show us the goods.

109
00:08:46,260 --> 00:08:49,970
Just what are you trying to leech
out of this country?!

110
00:08:50,220 --> 00:08:51,510
Is Nami safe...?

111
00:08:51,510 --> 00:08:53,970
Did she get away okay?

112
00:08:54,470 --> 00:08:58,430
Behind the Medi Assembly Hall
Alubarna North Block

113
00:09:01,440 --> 00:09:02,900
They finally came off.

114
00:09:03,270 --> 00:09:07,860
So this is what he meant
by a powerful one-shot attack.

115
00:09:09,110 --> 00:09:12,570
The wave of rebels is
just around the corner...

116
00:09:17,160 --> 00:09:19,120
though the situation has changed.

117
00:09:19,120 --> 00:09:21,120
For now, I should head to the palace.

118
00:09:26,340 --> 00:09:28,050
What's going on with Vivi?

119
00:09:28,050 --> 00:09:30,880
The battle seems to have started.

120
00:09:31,720 --> 00:09:33,470
Oh yeah, Vivi.

121
00:09:33,470 --> 00:09:35,180
Don't forget this:

122
00:09:35,890 --> 00:09:39,350
After a battle, that guy eats tons.

123
00:09:39,850 --> 00:09:41,140
I won't.

124
00:09:41,140 --> 00:09:43,810
We'll be waiting for you
in Alubarna, okay?!

125
00:09:43,810 --> 00:09:47,150
Yeah!

126
00:09:47,150 --> 00:09:49,530
This is do-or-die now.

127
00:09:51,900 --> 00:09:53,110
So don't screw up!

128
00:09:53,740 --> 00:09:55,120
Let's go!

129
00:09:55,120 --> 00:09:57,330
See you at Alubarna Palace!

130
00:10:08,880 --> 00:10:09,880
Chaka!

131
00:10:15,890 --> 00:10:17,640
In my book...

132
00:10:18,060 --> 00:10:19,890
weakness is a crime.

133
00:10:23,730 --> 00:10:24,770
Vivi!

134
00:10:31,110 --> 00:10:37,070
Palace Square
25 Minutes Until the Explosion

135
00:10:41,540 --> 00:10:43,540
K... Koza!

136
00:10:50,840 --> 00:10:51,920
It's you...

137
00:10:51,920 --> 00:10:54,630
Oh, you came using your old shortcut!

138
00:10:56,340 --> 00:10:58,640
Is something wrong with my eyes?

139
00:11:09,440 --> 00:11:12,570
I had intended to negotiate peace
with the Royal Army, but...

140
00:11:14,990 --> 00:11:15,910
Chaka...

141
00:11:17,360 --> 00:11:19,580
Our country's hero...

142
00:11:19,910 --> 00:11:22,790
is about to execute the king.

143
00:11:22,790 --> 00:11:25,000
It's hard to believe what I'm seeing.

144
00:11:27,960 --> 00:11:30,960
Well, isn't this interesting?

145
00:11:30,960 --> 00:11:38,140
As the battle rages around us,
the leaders of both sides are facing off.

146
00:11:38,140 --> 00:11:43,020
This war has become a death match
between two headless lizards.

147
00:11:45,810 --> 00:11:47,560
You seem confused.

148
00:11:47,560 --> 00:11:51,270
Well, that's just a natural reaction,
but it's actually simple.

149
00:11:52,820 --> 00:11:57,400
Just imagine the worst
possible scenario.

150
00:12:01,870 --> 00:12:05,540
Don't hold to suspicion, Koza.

151
00:12:12,500 --> 00:12:15,010
Do you love this country?

152
00:12:23,180 --> 00:12:25,850
Yeah! It's my homeland!

153
00:12:26,480 --> 00:12:28,310
I feel the same!

154
00:12:29,850 --> 00:12:30,940
Koza, listen–

155
00:12:30,940 --> 00:12:32,190
Vivi!

156
00:12:32,190 --> 00:12:34,940
Who stole this country's rain?!

157
00:12:37,030 --> 00:12:38,150
Everything was–

158
00:12:38,150 --> 00:12:40,160
It was me, Koza.

159
00:12:41,030 --> 00:12:45,870
Everything you thought
was the king's doing...

160
00:12:45,870 --> 00:12:48,870
was a trap laid by
my company and me.

161
00:12:48,870 --> 00:12:54,340
Over the last two years,
you all played right into our hands...

162
00:12:55,630 --> 00:13:01,300
all as the royal family and their army
desperately chased our fleeting shadows.

163
00:13:07,060 --> 00:13:11,770
You could've died
blissfully ignorant of the truth.

164
00:13:18,240 --> 00:13:20,740
Don't listen to him, Koza!

165
00:13:21,990 --> 00:13:23,070
Your Majesty...

166
00:13:23,490 --> 00:13:26,240
There are still things you can do!

167
00:13:26,240 --> 00:13:29,040
Save as many citizens as you can!

168
00:13:30,710 --> 00:13:32,500
In less than half an hour,

169
00:13:32,960 --> 00:13:35,960
the palace square will be blown up!

170
00:13:36,380 --> 00:13:37,590
What?!

171
00:13:38,090 --> 00:13:40,550
So you're still alive?

172
00:13:44,970 --> 00:13:48,020
Hurry!

173
00:13:58,900 --> 00:14:00,320
Stop!

174
00:14:02,400 --> 00:14:03,860
Vivi!

175
00:14:04,240 --> 00:14:07,030
Hey! Move, Vivi!
What are you doing?!

176
00:14:07,030 --> 00:14:09,040
The square will become a battlefield!

177
00:14:09,040 --> 00:14:10,370
If it really gets blown up–

178
00:14:10,370 --> 00:14:14,290
I won't let it! I won't let it
become a battlefield.

179
00:14:17,500 --> 00:14:20,590
Look at how you're panicking now.

180
00:14:20,590 --> 00:14:25,470
How do you think they'll all react
if they know the fate of the square?

181
00:14:25,470 --> 00:14:28,680
It won't end with just a panic.

182
00:14:29,310 --> 00:14:31,020
After such an event...

183
00:14:31,020 --> 00:14:32,810
the war won't stop!

184
00:14:32,810 --> 00:14:34,020
We won't save anyone!

185
00:14:38,230 --> 00:14:39,940
Isn't that right?

186
00:14:40,440 --> 00:14:43,950
Well, aren't you clever?

187
00:14:44,320 --> 00:14:47,450
It was obvious from the start
what we needed to do.

188
00:14:50,240 --> 00:14:53,370
We needed to stop
this orchestrated rebellion!

189
00:14:54,920 --> 00:14:56,420
And right now,

190
00:14:56,420 --> 00:14:58,920
you're the only one who can do it!

191
00:15:18,110 --> 00:15:23,030
Did you think I would just
sit back and watch?

192
00:15:34,660 --> 00:15:35,580
Chaka!

193
00:15:38,210 --> 00:15:39,460
I am...

194
00:15:39,880 --> 00:15:42,300
the Jackal, Alabasta's guardian deity!

195
00:15:42,300 --> 00:15:45,380
The one who destroys the enemies
of the royal family!

196
00:15:47,470 --> 00:15:50,640
If I can still draw breath, I can fight!

197
00:15:51,560 --> 00:15:54,270
And that is what you call "stupidity."

198
00:15:54,600 --> 00:15:56,940
You two should do as you need!

199
00:15:56,940 --> 00:16:00,270
I can hold him back
for at least a few more minutes!

200
00:16:00,860 --> 00:16:01,770
Okay!

201
00:16:03,440 --> 00:16:04,570
Chaka!

202
00:16:04,570 --> 00:16:07,780
Seems the Sand-Sand Clan's
leader isn't all that strong.

203
00:16:12,120 --> 00:16:13,700
Now, what's the matter?

204
00:16:18,710 --> 00:16:20,960
Ouch!

205
00:16:21,500 --> 00:16:25,260
What gives?! I'm just a kid!
Go easy on me!

206
00:16:25,260 --> 00:16:27,510
What a pain in the neck.

207
00:16:28,090 --> 00:16:32,470
You're the one who
asked me to train you.

208
00:16:46,650 --> 00:16:48,950
Report from guard unit #2
to headquarters!

209
00:16:49,910 --> 00:16:51,910
Report from unit #2 to headquarters!

210
00:16:51,910 --> 00:16:54,910
The fourth line... has been breached!

211
00:16:57,120 --> 00:17:00,620
The Rebel Army passed the central plaza
toward the north block!

212
00:17:00,620 --> 00:17:02,000
They'll reach the palace!

213
00:17:02,630 --> 00:17:04,340
Raise the white flag!

214
00:17:05,170 --> 00:17:09,170
Surrender now, Royal Army!

215
00:17:09,170 --> 00:17:11,550
What is Her Highness saying?

216
00:17:11,550 --> 00:17:12,680
Surrender?!

217
00:17:12,680 --> 00:17:16,140
If we do that, what will
become of this country?!

218
00:17:16,890 --> 00:17:18,520
Hey, look!

219
00:17:18,520 --> 00:17:19,600
That's...!

220
00:17:20,100 --> 00:17:21,480
It's Koza!

221
00:17:21,480 --> 00:17:24,310
Why is the leader
of the Rebel Army here?!

222
00:17:24,940 --> 00:17:27,730
Please listen to Vivi!

223
00:17:27,730 --> 00:17:31,410
We no longer desire victory,
much less a fight!

224
00:17:31,410 --> 00:17:34,120
We must cease this battle!

225
00:17:34,120 --> 00:17:36,700
– What?
– What's going on?

226
00:17:37,790 --> 00:17:43,380
I will let the Rebel Army know
that this battle was pointless...

227
00:17:44,460 --> 00:17:48,050
That there's no longer
a reason for us to fight!

228
00:17:48,760 --> 00:17:54,010
In order to end this pointless shedding
of blood, wave the white flag!

229
00:17:54,010 --> 00:17:55,430
I beg you!

230
00:17:56,260 --> 00:17:59,220
The king's head is close at hand!

231
00:18:00,230 --> 00:18:02,690
We can see the clock tower!

232
00:18:08,780 --> 00:18:11,320
We're approaching the palace square!

233
00:18:11,820 --> 00:18:14,280
Prepare to attack!

234
00:18:23,580 --> 00:18:24,920
H-Hold it!

235
00:18:32,550 --> 00:18:34,050
White flags?!

236
00:18:34,930 --> 00:18:39,560
The Royal Army is waving
white flags to surrender!

237
00:18:43,940 --> 00:18:45,690
Koza!

238
00:18:45,690 --> 00:18:48,860
The battle is over!

239
00:18:48,860 --> 00:18:50,360
Troops!

240
00:18:50,360 --> 00:18:53,320
Quell your anger
and drop your weapons!

241
00:18:54,280 --> 00:18:57,950
The Royal Army no longer
has the will to fight!

242
00:19:01,240 --> 00:19:02,580
Let this be the end...!

243
00:19:19,720 --> 00:19:21,720
Is that true, Koza?

244
00:19:22,100 --> 00:19:25,100
Yeah, the battle is now...

245
00:19:41,910 --> 00:19:47,080
Koza!

246
00:19:51,380 --> 00:19:53,300
Koza!

247
00:19:54,510 --> 00:19:59,550
We'll build an awesome city that'll
increase this country's greenery!

248
00:20:00,300 --> 00:20:01,430
For sure!

249
00:20:12,270 --> 00:20:15,360
R-Rebel Army...!

250
00:20:16,740 --> 00:20:19,320
D-Don't... fight!

251
00:20:19,320 --> 00:20:26,250
– Koza!
– Koza!

252
00:20:26,250 --> 00:20:28,290
How dare you shoot Koza?!

253
00:20:28,290 --> 00:20:29,830
Get them!

254
00:20:35,460 --> 00:20:37,340
Baroque Works!

255
00:20:45,220 --> 00:20:48,230
You! Why'd you shoot Koza?!

256
00:20:56,070 --> 00:20:58,400
Rebel Army...

257
00:20:58,400 --> 00:21:00,110
L-Listen to me...

258
00:21:02,120 --> 00:21:03,120
What's going on?!

259
00:21:03,830 --> 00:21:05,490
A sudden sandstorm!

260
00:21:07,040 --> 00:21:09,040
Rebel Army...!

261
00:21:13,380 --> 00:21:14,460
They opened fire!

262
00:21:14,960 --> 00:21:17,510
Those bastards...!

263
00:21:24,390 --> 00:21:26,890
What's with this dust devil?!

264
00:21:26,890 --> 00:21:28,350
We can't see a thing!

265
00:21:33,520 --> 00:21:35,730
Damn those bastards!

266
00:21:41,030 --> 00:21:42,410
Don't fire at random!

267
00:21:42,410 --> 00:21:43,620
What's going on?!

268
00:21:44,240 --> 00:21:45,990
It's simple.

269
00:21:46,620 --> 00:21:51,790
Baroque Works members
have infiltrated both armies.

270
00:21:57,170 --> 00:21:58,260
No!

271
00:21:58,670 --> 00:22:00,760
Hey! Hang in there!

272
00:22:08,100 --> 00:22:10,350
Surrender, my ass!

273
00:22:10,980 --> 00:22:13,850
Launching a surprise attack
while the white flag is up?!

274
00:22:14,600 --> 00:22:17,820
Is this how the Royal Army fights?!

275
00:22:18,150 --> 00:22:20,030
How could they stoop so low?!

276
00:22:25,780 --> 00:22:28,790
Please! Stop, everyone!

277
00:22:28,790 --> 00:22:30,000
Don't fight!

278
00:22:30,540 --> 00:22:33,000
Listen to me!

279
00:22:35,580 --> 00:22:38,840
S... Stop... Rebel Army...

280
00:22:38,840 --> 00:22:41,670
This battle is...

281
00:22:56,350 --> 00:22:57,440
Are you okay?!

282
00:22:59,270 --> 00:23:01,860
Royal Army,
launch the counteroffensive!

283
00:23:34,270 --> 00:23:35,230
Stop...!

284
00:23:35,730 --> 00:23:37,020
Stop already...

285
00:23:39,980 --> 00:23:40,940
Please...

286
00:23:42,360 --> 00:23:44,190
Stop...

287
00:23:44,950 --> 00:23:47,820
You fought well, young lady.

288
00:23:48,530 --> 00:23:49,660
But...

289
00:23:50,200 --> 00:23:52,870
your voice will no longer reach them.

290
00:23:55,580 --> 00:23:57,290
So this is it...

291
00:24:02,250 --> 00:24:03,840
Run, Vivi!

292
00:24:04,210 --> 00:24:07,380
Get away from him!

293
00:24:15,140 --> 00:24:16,140
No.

294
00:24:21,820 --> 00:24:25,280
This dust devil...
is your doing, isn't it?

295
00:24:27,570 --> 00:24:28,570
I can still...

296
00:24:30,660 --> 00:24:34,490
If I stop the attack that's scheduled
to happen in fifteen minutes,

297
00:24:35,160 --> 00:24:37,120
I can at least mitigate casualties!

298
00:24:42,460 --> 00:24:45,210
If we do this, the rebellion will stop.

299
00:24:45,210 --> 00:24:47,720
If we do that, the rebellion will stop.

300
00:24:48,170 --> 00:24:50,800
Wake up, Princess.

301
00:24:51,800 --> 00:24:55,640
I can't stand your wide-eyed idealism.

302
00:24:59,100 --> 00:25:04,730
Only those with power
can speak of realizing ideals.

303
00:25:05,530 --> 00:25:08,610
And you have been found wanting!

304
00:25:11,820 --> 00:25:14,030
I don't care if it's annoying.

305
00:25:15,200 --> 00:25:17,370
I won't give up on my ideals!

306
00:25:20,210 --> 00:25:22,540
You could never understand!

307
00:25:23,040 --> 00:25:25,800
I'm the princess of this country.

308
00:25:25,800 --> 00:25:27,510
I'll never give in to you!

309
00:25:33,010 --> 00:25:35,470
You're not cute at all.

310
00:25:36,680 --> 00:25:38,680
You think I'll give up?

311
00:25:39,350 --> 00:25:40,440
I will...

312
00:25:43,400 --> 00:25:47,110
I will... save this country...!

313
00:25:53,820 --> 00:25:54,910
Vivi!

314
00:25:59,580 --> 00:26:02,580
Fifteen minutes
until the square is blown up.

315
00:26:03,330 --> 00:26:08,550
The backup rebel forces will continue
to pour into this place.

316
00:26:09,260 --> 00:26:14,840
One after another, all without
realizing their own fate...

317
00:26:24,940 --> 00:26:29,900
Had you let the Royal Army know about
the explosion in the square earlier—

318
00:26:29,900 --> 00:26:31,900
even if there had been a panic—

319
00:26:31,900 --> 00:26:36,200
you could've saved thousands,
maybe tens of thousands of lives.

320
00:26:37,910 --> 00:26:39,160
Stop!

321
00:26:39,160 --> 00:26:41,870
Please stop it, Crocodile!

322
00:26:45,830 --> 00:26:50,840
In the end, your optimistic ideals
about saving everything...

323
00:26:50,840 --> 00:26:56,760
will result in the deaths
of the citizens you love so much.

324
00:27:02,350 --> 00:27:08,190
From start to finish,
the people in this country...

325
00:27:08,190 --> 00:27:11,320
never failed to keep me entertained.

326
00:27:19,740 --> 00:27:25,330
You did a fine job spying on
my company these last two years.

327
00:27:27,330 --> 00:27:29,750
It's me! Don't you recognize me?

328
00:27:31,000 --> 00:27:32,920
I suppose I can't blame you.

329
00:27:32,920 --> 00:27:34,880
I did lose some weight...

330
00:27:36,890 --> 00:27:40,850
But in the end, you and your allies
couldn't stop a thing!

331
00:27:42,020 --> 00:27:45,560
Stopping the rebellion...
Saving the kingdom...

332
00:27:45,560 --> 00:27:49,520
Your worthless ideals did nothing...

333
00:27:49,520 --> 00:27:52,730
but create more unnecessary victims.

334
00:27:54,990 --> 00:27:56,860
Let me tell you something.

335
00:27:58,660 --> 00:28:00,990
You can't save this country.

336
00:28:03,450 --> 00:28:05,410
Goodbye, Princess.

337
00:28:50,330 --> 00:28:51,630
It can't be...

338
00:28:53,040 --> 00:28:56,800
Crocodile!

339
00:29:00,720 --> 00:29:02,350
Luffy!

340
00:29:05,060 --> 00:29:07,270
Straw Hat...!
